# Project Manager

Manage your GitHub backlog with agent-powered grooming.
{% if github_repo %}
Default repo: {{ github_repo }}
{% endif %}

## Prerequisites

- [GitHub CLI](https://cli.github.com/) installed and authenticated (`gh auth login`)

## Usage

```
/skill:project-manager triage
/skill:project-manager groom #42
/skill:project-manager sprint
/skill:project-manager stale
/skill:project-manager report
```

Or use the `/pm` command directly.

## Label Schema

| Category | Labels |
|----------|--------|
| Type | `bug`, `feature`, `enhancement`, `question`, `docs`, `chore` |
| Priority | `priority:critical`, `priority:high`, `priority:medium`, `priority:low` |
| Size | `size:xs`, `size:s`, `size:m`, `size:l`, `size:xl` |
